# Workspace-wide ignores

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Build output
**/.next/
**/out/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.wrangler/
**/.vercel/
**/.turbo/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.dev.vars
**/.dev.vars*
